result.text: October 11th witnessed the grand opening of the "2023 China Digital Music Industry Summit" in the vibrant Huli District of #Xiamen. A conglomerate of national and international mavens from the digital music industry, encompassing scholars, industry stalwarts, and innovators, converged to delve into the prospective trajectories of China’s digital music industry, aiming to spearhead its high-caliber evolution. The "2022 China Digital Music Industry Report," an inaugural expose of its kind, was unfurled during the assembly.
